{"tid":972003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大嶼山神樂院神父疑行山失蹤一晚　職員稱已尋回","createTime":"2019-01-07T05:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T15:55:01.000Z","uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e60e821dc1bb8c506740377e53d38897100c7da3","tid":972003,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"莫非喺上帝感召？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n康姓神父失蹤一晚後，今早於大嶼山北梅窩碼頭被尋回。他沒有受傷，清醒送往北大嶼山醫院治理。警方相信事件沒有可疑。根據地圖，聖母神樂院至梅窩碼頭相距約4.2公里，徒步行走須時逾1小時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190107/s00001/1546826133298/%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E5%B1%B1%E7%A5%9E%E6%A8%82%E9%99%A2%E7%A5%9E%E7%88%B6%E7%96%91%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%B1%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E4%B8%80%E6%99%9A-%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E5%B0%8B%E5%9B%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190107%2Fs00001%2F1546826133298%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25A5%259E%25E6%25A8%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%2588%25B6%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2599%259A-%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%259B%259E&d=CLvBSNi7HEDZp085ZmrW7jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=184489c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190107%2Fs00001%2F1546826133298%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25A5%259E%25E6%25A8%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%2588%25B6%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2599%259A-%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%259B%259E&h=dfeacc9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190107/s00001/1546826133298/%E5%A4%A7%E